{"tid":2420052,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"德國內政部據報去信國會 指中國政府試圖威嚇居德港人","createTime":"2021-02-23T15:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T00:11:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fd065a9feccb503604590141f74e747269a0d867","tid":2420052,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:52:34.000Z","msg":"德國內政部據報去信國會人權事務委員會負責人，表示自從香港前年爆發反修例示威以來，中國政府試圖威嚇居於德國的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述信件指出，自反修例示威開始以來，身處德國、為中方辦事的人，不斷試圖影響公眾輿論以支持中國政府，並針對支持示威活動的人。<br />\n<br />\n信中提到，前年8月17日漢堡一場支持香港示威者的活動，有親中人士到場拍片及影相，估計是出於恐嚇目的，又指目前大約有720名港人，獲許可在德國居留。<br />\n<br />\n有自由民主黨成員說，德國政府是時候意識到，為中國政府辦事的人，可能對流亡的港人構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577083-20210223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577083-20210223.htm&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpmwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=3aa3bd1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577083-20210223.htm&h=ef8cc0c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577083-20210223.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f6c11ff38ffad51b3303de4cb703ce3688b7df39","tid":2420052,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb4d5c7f4dde5d47badd5d98ac3989ff2548c9d","tid":2420052,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85477356f6a81a84521831d2a5ffb1ea5c2cb94b","tid":2420052,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598d93add72543ec75c53b0b93c52abc43d52299","tid":2420052,"uid":183844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:03:14.000Z","msg":"走咗仲搞嘅話<br />\n不過係驚手足喺德國組織啫<br />\n換句說話即係做任何嘢都可以加呢個咁嘅質疑<br />\n對外國政府嚟講好大獲<br />\n如果真係要令中共相信無任何組織力<br />\n大概真係要遊手好閒乜都唔做毫無生產力<br />\n總之要如似廢人一個咁啦<br />\n但外國政府願意養廢人嗎？<br />\n接收香港精英<br />\n最可觀嘅利益就係希望可以喺外國發展<br />\n從而得到利益<br />\n咁樣睇到中共嘅行動如果成功<br />\n即係全世界嘅經濟都可以由中共控制<br />\n更不論係香港人定係外國本地人"},{"pid":"aced31f0227e5536c315036630f98ec15f7a78f0","tid":2420052,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"開始轉對中共立場"},{"pid":"c482ef4f5e82a38c6e7a096f58c4e99650789fb0","tid":2420052,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acda9e9d0c2378c4de6d0b0ef676e97899055dbf","tid":2420052,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3d718dd6561f75451dacb07a0d67533cb117e2","tid":2420052,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd065a9feccb503604590141f74e747269a0d867","tid":2420052,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:52:34.000Z","msg":"德國內政部據報去信國會人權事務委員會負責人，表示自從香港前年爆發反修例示威以來，中國政府試圖威嚇居於德國的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述信件指出，自反修例示威開始以來，身處德國、為中方辦事的人，不斷試圖影響公眾輿論以支持中國政府，並針對支持示威活動的人。<br />\n<br />\n信中提到，前年8月17日漢堡一場支持香港示威者的活動，有親中人士到場拍片及影相，估計是出於恐嚇目的，又指目前大約有720名港人，獲許可在德國居留。<br />\n<br />\n有自由民主黨成員說，德國政府是時候意識到，為中國政府辦事的人，可能對流亡的港人構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577083-20210223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2F